 Reduces number of rows produced by joins when optimizer detects that duplicated
 join output rows can be skipped.
+
+``optimizer.plan-with-table-node-partitioning``
+^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
+
+* **Type:** ``boolean``
+* **Default value:** ``true``
+
+Use connector provided table node partitioning when reading tables.
+When set to ``true`` each table partition is read by a separate node.
+Partition reader assignments are distributed across worker nodes for
+parallel processing.
